{"tid":1783271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動]你哋重記唔記得721呀！！","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T15:07:37.000Z","uid":170014,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2dfaf572255a9f6e983367efd71ed524c6b77d","tid":1783271,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下個禮拜六就係元朗恐襲五個月啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重記唔記得當日嘅畫面呀 到呢一刻我重歷歷在目</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67y1aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67y1aab.jpg&h=cb54227b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QRRxoy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QRRxoy.jpg&h=16113057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次元朗恐襲四個月喺區選前幾日 大家都唔想喺嗰段時間行動 我明 我知香港人係一定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔會忘記</span>嗰一日<br />\n<br />\n今次撞正係禮拜六 係集會遊行嘅好時機 <br />\n<br />\n我有兩個建議畀大家<br />\n<br />\n建議一：搞一個徹查元朗恐襲大遊行 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我懇請有團體或素人去搞 思穎妹妹都做到 我相信大家都一定做到</span></span> 重記唔記得 7 8月嗰陣搞遊行 搞到要排期呀 我哋唔可以畀佢停<br />\n<br />\n優點：喺元朗度搞有象徵意義 喚醒香港人嘅憤怒<br />\n缺點：地理位置差 唔熟地班嘅話好易比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n建議二：黨鐵商場和你坐<br />\n<br />\n根據上幾個月嘅經驗 元朗站2點就會閂 yoho 都好早收 元朗都極多狗 唔好太留戀危險嘅地點 即使個地點有象徵意義 君子不立危牆之下 喺黨鐵商場坐 嗯排商場因為聖誕都好旺 如果無咗一日生意都幾係嘢  <br />\n<br />\n優點：比較上安全 可經濟攬抄<br />\n缺點：主題性唔夠大 令人以為係普通示威活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">討論完嗰陣就係時候做文宣 無乜幾多時間咋！！！</span>"},{"pid":"2cb1615c778384ac4b7ea91ff18cf2c61c412569","tid":1783271,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nbtw 依家要多啲文宣呀! 有低門檻玩法, 入嚟睇吓啦!<br />\n[行動] 解決目前文宣困局--A4 size label 周圍貼! 人人都係文宣組!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783119</a>"},{"pid":"0eef3a1f5c3e8e97f2267c1adc015ee6090e02d0","tid":1783271,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85417e1d85328e818fa1aa08474e4c4d0a4c8b9","tid":1783271,"uid":39984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:00:08.000Z","msg":"幫推！<br />\n兩個方案都贊成，會出席！"},{"pid":"775fb406dab36980e5b902ab3ddb0a94be9482f0","tid":1783271,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"無忘721"},{"pid":"1f1518a6384fe37aeaf5bd0e6fdd50e7e2bed2ba","tid":1783271,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8FZGo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8FZGo0.jpg&h=6fef6411&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XzDcvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XzDcvG.jpg&h=316a2610&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wcdLQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wcdLQG.jpg&h=a5b76cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBz3731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBz3731.jpg&h=3443a102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1837972df962bf8e0d571b2aea092ba6dc7fc84","tid":1783271,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"勿忘721"},{"pid":"a7dd7410c9b85e880fd7baa649fa487247bb39e6","tid":1783271,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"721 831 101 1111"},{"pid":"b1ea06c158b723fbad4e719b8d4ab3075335d50b","tid":1783271,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"556f42eade47d93ed930356836d1ac03137bc5fa","tid":1